---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Callout from '../components/Callout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Workshops"
  description="Invite Senior Security to deliver a practical scam-awareness workshop for your community."
  canonicalPath="/workshops"
  intro="Our sessions are interactive, respectful, and built for real-world decisions."
>
  <section class="section-space pb-0 space-y-6">
    <article class="panel p-8 prose">
      <h2>What a workshop includes</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Common scam patterns explained in plain language.</li>
        <li>Practice spotting red flags in calls, emails, and texts.</li>
        <li>Simple scripts for verifying people and organizations safely.</li>
        <li>Printable checklists for participants and caregivers.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>What participants learn</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>How to pause when pressure or urgency appears.</li>
        <li>How to verify before sharing personal information.</li>
        <li>What payment methods are hard to recover and why.</li>
        <li>How to report fraud and ask for support without shame.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

